<html><body><span style="padding-left:150px;"><h4>Beepsend Gateway  Instruction Process</h4></span><br><ul><li>If User has an existing Beepsend account then login into account by clicking on the following link <a style="color:blue;font-weight:bold;" target="_blank" href="http://signup.beepsend.com/">Click here</a>. <b>--(this will be a link button which will be redirected to the Beepsend login page)</b></li><li>If a User does not have any Beepsend account then he first needs to Signup with Beepsend by clicking on the following link <a style="color:blue;font-weight:bold;" target="_blank" href="http://signup.beepsend.com/">Click here</a> providing the Valid mobile number. Once the account has been created just login into Beepsend account.</li><li>Click on <b>Connections</b> at setting page. <b>API Token</b> value will be displayed.</li><li>Copy that API Token and paste it in the <b>Token</b> field textbox in your salesforce Organisation.</li><li>In the <b>From</b> field textbox User will be providing the Registered mobile number which is available on 2-Way Numbers section with Beepsend account.</li></ul></body></html>